%% ==========================================================
%% Subject:        Login + worker-JWT routing (with backup-node lane)
%% Authoritative:  spec/19/12-jwt-delivery-contract.md + 04-worker-routing.md + 18-backup-nodes.md
%% Status:         Illustrative only. If this diagram disagrees
%%                 with the authoritative spec(s) above, the
%%                 spec wins and this file is the bug.
%% Banner version: 2.0.0 (2026-05-06, Phase 13.3 — refreshed for:
%%                 (a) UserDirectory lookup at Main (no password at Main, per 03-§2.x + 05-§2.1);
%%                 (b) credentialed body proxied to Worker for verification;
%%                 (c) backup-node lane: backups EXCLUDED from routing (D9, 04-§1.4).
%% ==========================================================
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant React as React Frontend
    participant Main as Main Server
    participant Cache as Main Cache
    participant DB as Main SQLite (Root tier)
    participant Worker as Worker Node (primary)
    participant Backup as Worker Node (IsBackup=1)

    React->>Main: POST /API/V1/Auth/Login<br/>X-Correlation-Id, X-Idempotency-Key, X-Auth-Action: Login<br/>{ Email, Password }
    Main->>DB: SELECT CompanyId, WorkerNodeId FROM UserDirectory WHERE UserEmail=?
    Note over Main,DB: Main MUST NOT verify passwords / TOTP.<br/>UserDirectory holds NO secrets (03-§2.x).
    Main->>Cache: GET MainWorker:Company:{id}:WorkerNodeId
    alt cache hit
        Cache-->>Main: WorkerNodeId
    else cache miss
        Main->>DB: SELECT WorkerNodeEndpoint FROM WorkerNode WHERE WorkerNodeId=? AND IsBackup=0
        DB-->>Main: WorkerNodeEndpoint
        Main->>Cache: SET TTL=MainWorker.Cache.CompanyToWorkerTtlSeconds (default 900s)
    end
    Note over Backup: Backup nodes (IsBackup=1) are EXCLUDED from every routing strategy (D9, 04-§1.4).<br/>They mirror data via 19-incremental-backup-sync but never serve live traffic.
    Main->>Worker: POST /API/V1/Auth/VerifyCredential (proxy)<br/>{ Email, Password } + X-Correlation-Id
    Worker->>Worker: Verify PasswordHash + TOTP against AppUser (App tier)
    Worker-->>Main: 200 { Verified: true, Has2FAEnabled, UnusedBackupCodes }
    alt 2FA on
        Main-->>React: 200 JSON { Step: AwaitTotp, ChallengeId, PartialAuthJwt }
        React->>Main: POST /API/V1/Auth/TwoFactor/Verify { Code, ChallengeId }
        Main->>Worker: proxy TOTP verify
        Worker-->>Main: 200 / 403
        alt UnusedBackupCodes == 0
            Main-->>React: 403 { Error.SubCode: TotpBackupExhausted }<br/>X-Auth-Action: RegenerateBackupCodes
        end
    end
    Main->>Main: Mint RS256 worker JWT (sub, cmp, wnk, aud=worker, exp<=WorkerJwtTtlSeconds, roles, jti, kid)
    Main-->>React: 200 JSON { WorkerEndpoint, WorkerJwt, JwtExpiresAt }
    Note over React: JWT in JSON body only — never cookie / localStorage / URL.<br/>Stored IN-MEMORY (useRef / non-persistent store) per 12-§2. CSP per §5.

    Note over React,Worker: Subsequent business calls bypass Main
    React->>Worker: GET /API/V1/Company/{slug}<br/>Authorization: Bearer <WorkerJwt>
    Worker->>Worker: Verify RS256 sig, kid, exp(skew=60s), aud, wnk, iss (12-§7)
    Worker-->>React: 200 (data)

    Note over Worker,Backup: Async replication only — backup never appears in WorkerEndpoint responses.
    Worker-->>Backup: incremental sync (19-§4)
